STEP BY STEP 🎶 (day by day… IYKYK 😂)

Going darker or wanting more dimension? This is what you ask for or what you do!

👉Step 1: Root blend… blend those roots, don’t drag the color just feather it a bit!
👉Step 2: Weave Low Lights… the size and spacing will determine how dimensional your color will be!
👉Step 3: Apply… pulling through the ends will give you more dimension, dragging them 1/2-3/4 down will leave more brightness on the tips!
👉Step 4: Balayage… (optional) you would do this if you wanted pops of dimension or to bring up dimension higher up in the hair

STYLING PRODUCTS 👇👇👇

Products are KEY and will help you recreate your style when you leave the salon!

So WHAT ARE SOME KEY PRODUCTS⁉️👇
- You ALWAYS need professional shampoo & conditioner. This will help your color last. Store bought products will speed up fading and dryness!
- Pairing a cream styling product and an oil will help keep your ends hydrated. The more hydrated they are, the less breakage you will have, and the less it breaks the less you will have to trim which means, the longer it will grow!
- You need a FINISHING styling product. This will lock in that style and help it last longer, this can be hair spray, texture spray, shine spray.
